{"article_id":"MbkhzmWHWUngkF0I","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Why did Donald Trump fire FBI Director James Comey so abruptly , in such humiliating fashion , with no plan","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to communicate the reasoning behind the move","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"and no list of replacements ready ?","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"It is the question","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"that launched a thousand think pieces .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Even Trump surrogates were not prepared to answer it .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Sean Spicer literally hid in the bushes","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"( sorry , among the bushes ) .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"The thing is , the answer is pretty obvious .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"The implications are terrifying ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"but the motivations are not complicated .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"He was mad","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that people on his TV keep talking about the Russia investigation .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"He was mad","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Comey didn ' t back him up on his ludicrous claims","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"that President Obama wiretapped Trump Tower ,","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"even when people on his TV were criticizing him for it .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"He was mad","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"Comey hasn ' t been more loyal ,","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"convinced","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"Comey was to blame for his bad ratings .","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"So he fired Comey .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"That ' s the picture","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"the Washington Post paints","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"( with 30 sources ! ) ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"as well as Politico .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"But it remains extremely difficult to accept or internalize .","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"Why is it so hard to accept that Trump is acting out of pique , on impulse ,","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"because Comey on his TV gave him bad feels ?","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"In child psychology , \" theory of mind \" refers to a basic capacity","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"humans develop around the age of 2 or 3","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"to recognize","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"that other people are independent agents , distinct minds , with their own beliefs , desires , fears , etc .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"We learn to \" read \" behaviors as evidence of those internal states .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"And","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"because we are relentless pattern seekers ,","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"we are constantly developing theories of people ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"seeking to explain what they do through reference to their beliefs and plans .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"This has badly misled us with Trump .","depth":4},{"id":39,"text":"Much of the dialogue around him , the journalism and analysis , even the statements of his own surrogates , amounts to a desperate attempt","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"to construct a Theory of Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"to explain what he does and says through some story about his long-term goals and beliefs .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"We badly want to understand Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"to grasp him .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"It might give us some sense of control ,","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"or at least an ability","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"to predict what he will do next .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"But what if there ' s nothing","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"to understand ?","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"What if there ' s no there there ?","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"What if our attempts","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"to explain Trump","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"have failed","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"not because we haven ' t hit on the right one ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"but because we are , theory-of-mind-wise , overinterpreting the text ?","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"In short , what if Trump is exactly as he appears :","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"a hopeless narcissist with the attention span of a fruit fly ,","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"unable to maintain consistent beliefs or commitments from moment to moment ,","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"acting on base instinct , entirely situationally ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"to bolster his terrifyingly fragile ego .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"There is clearly something wrong with Trump .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"But exactly what he is","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"- or ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"if you prefer to medicalize it ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"what he has -","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"is a matter of some controversy .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"In a recent Rolling Stone article , Alex Morris explores the battle within the field of psychiatry over whether to diagnose Trump at a distance .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"( ' s own Brian Resnick also has a great piece on it . )","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"The nub of the disagreement comes down to whether Trump has a disorder .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"There are nine traits","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"used to identify narcissistic personality disorder","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"( things like \" requires excessive admiration \"","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"and \" has a grandiose sense of self-importance \" ) .","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"Fitting five or more is considered sufficient for diagnosis .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"All nine describe Trump ' s public behavior with eerie accuracy .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"But a disorder , by definition , inhibits normal functioning ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"impedes success .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"And Trump is inarguably successful .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"He ' s one of the most powerful people in the world .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"Whatever kind of personality he may have ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"some psychiatrists argue ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"he can ' t have a disorder .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"He ' s doing well for himself .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"Whether you see this as evidence of Trump ' s fitness","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"or evidence of the power of inherited wealth in America ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"I ' m not sure","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"it makes much difference from a citizen ' s point of view .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"Whether or not Trump has NPD ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"he clearly has the NP part .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Like all extreme narcissists , he feels a gnawing sense of inadequacy","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"and thus requires constant adulation , admiration , and reinforcement for his oversize , hypersensitive ego .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Like all extreme narcissists , he is exquisitely attuned to offense , to any hint","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"of being the dominated party or the loser , and incredibly vengeful","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"when he feels","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"he ' s been crossed","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"( which is frequently ) .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Like all extreme narcissists , he sees every interaction , every situation , as a zero-sum contest","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"in which there will be winners and losers .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"Like all extreme narcissists , he is prone to building a fantasy world","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"in which he is always on top , always the winner .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"And like all extreme narcissists , he sees other people only through the lens of how they reflect or affect him .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"But Trump is not merely a narcissist .","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"There are other things going on .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"Many narcissists are quite well-regulated .","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"Using other people to one ' s advantage takes not only in-the-moment charm","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"but an ability","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"to think ahead , as in a game of chess .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"Succeeding requires fooling other people ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"and fooling other people requires an ability","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"to hold a complex social map in one ' s head ,","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"to sustain a consistent performance over time .","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"Trump does have some crude cunning","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"to manipulate people in the moment .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"He can sense what they want","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"and what will elicit their approval .","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"But he lacks any ability","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"to hold beliefs , commitments , or even deceptions in his head across contexts .","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"( On Twitter , I compared him to a goldfish . )","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"He is utterly unable to step back","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"and put his gut emotions in larger perspective ,","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"to see himself as a person among people , in social contexts","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"that demand some adaptation .","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"He is impatient with attempts","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"to influence him to take a larger view","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"- he demands one-page memos , for instance .","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"Matt Yglesias says","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"that Trump lies all the time .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"And it ' s certainly true","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"that he says false things all the time .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"But even to say \" lie \" seems to suggest a certain self-awareness , an ability","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"to distinguish performance from reality ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"that Trump shows no signs","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"of possessing .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"Trump does have consistent attitudes ,","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"and that has given his actions some consistency .","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"Above all , he is utterly terrified of , and hostile to , weakness .","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"Fear of weakness helps explain","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"why Trump mocked John McCain","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"for being taken prisoner ,","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"why he mocked a disabled reporter ,","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"why he ' s been so consistently racist .","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"Somewhere in his reptile brain , he views being captured , disabled , or persecuted as weakness , as being dominated .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"It also explains his fondness for autocratic strongmen","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"- the ones","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"who dominate .","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"But these attitudes , these instincts , do not seem to yield persistent beliefs or principles .","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"Trump is highly attuned to dominance and submission in the moment ,","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"but each moment is a new moment ,","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"unconstrained by prior commitments , statements , or actions .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"Trump defies our theory of mind","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"because he appears to lack a coherent , persistent self or worldview .","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"He is a raging fire of need ,","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"protected and shaped by a lifetime of entitlement ,","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"with the emotional maturity and attention span of a 6-year-old ,","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"utterly unaware of the long-term implications of his actions .","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"We are not accustomed to having someone so obviously disordered in a position of such power .","depth":6},{"id":156,"text":"Trump is surrounded by people","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"- not only members of his administration","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"but Congress , the press , pundits , conservative ideological groups , industry lobbyists -","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"eager to invent stories","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"to make sense of his behavior .","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"Politicos and journalists need a story","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"in which Trump ' s stumbling and grasping can be construed as a savvy media strategy , a \" distraction \" from some other wrongdoing","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"he has going on ,","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"or a \" pivot \" from his current omnishambles .","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"Those are all versions of political maneuvering","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"with which they are familiar .","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"They need for Trump to want things ,","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"to be after things ,","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"to have a plan .","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"Politicians , journalists , analysts , the public - everyone wants some kind of story , some Theory of Trump .","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"And so Trump surrogates try to provide it ,","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"scrambling to weave a coherent narrative around his careening , erratic lies .","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"But there ' s no there there .","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"He ' s lunging this way and that , situation by situation .","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"Firing Comey ?","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"Trump just got mad .","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"He wanted Comey and the Russia investigation off his TV .","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"There ' s no deeper story than that .","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"This is an utterly terrifying conclusion .","depth":6},{"id":180,"text":"A Machiavellian Trump","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"- one","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"who was merely acting the fool ,","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"manipulating the public and media in service of some diabolical long-term agenda -","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"is less frightening than a purely narcissistic and impulsive one .","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"No agenda guides him ,","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"no past commitments or statements restrain him ,","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"so no one ,","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"not even his closest allies","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"( much less the American public or foreign governments )","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"can trust him , even for a second .","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"He will do what makes him feel dominant and respected , in the moment , with no consideration of anything else ,","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"not because he has chosen to reject other considerations ,","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"but because he is , by all appearances , incapable of considering them .","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"This makes him ,","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"as many others have noted ,","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"extremely vulnerable to being manipulated by whoever happens to talk to him last ,","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"whoever butters him up","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"and makes him feel important .","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"( And that includes the TV . )","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"It ' s one thing","depth":9},{"id":201,"text":"when that involves a wild Twitter accusation or the firing of a staff member .","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"All Trump ' s crises so far have been internal and self-inflicted , more or less .","depth":8},{"id":203,"text":"But what will happen","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"when he gets into a confrontation with North Korea ,","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"when Kim Jong Un deliberately provokes him ?","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"Will his response be considered and strategic ?","depth":12},{"id":207,"text":"Will he be able to get information and aid from allies ?","depth":13},{"id":208,"text":"Will he be able to make and keep commitments during negotiations ?","depth":13},{"id":209,"text":"More likely he will prove ,","depth":14},{"id":210,"text":"as he has in literally every confrontation of the past several years ,","depth":14},{"id":211,"text":"congenitally unable to back down or deescalate ,","depth":14},{"id":212,"text":"even if doing so is clearly in everyone ' s best interests .","depth":14},{"id":213,"text":"More likely he will be desperate to maintain face","depth":14},{"id":214,"text":"and will listen to whatever his security staff whispers in his ear .","depth":14},{"id":215,"text":"More likely he will make rash and fateful decisions with insufficient consultation and no clear plan .","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"That ' s who he is :","depth":10},{"id":217,"text":"a disregulated bundle of impulses ,","depth":11},{"id":218,"text":"being manipulated by a cast of crooks and incompetents ,","depth":12},{"id":219,"text":"supported by a Republican Party","depth":13},{"id":220,"text":"willing to bet the stability of the country against upper-income tax cuts .","depth":13},{"id":221,"text":"We need to stop looking for a more complicated story .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":443,"left":263,"right":442,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":263,"left":250,"right":262,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":229,"right":249,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":229,"left":224,"right":228,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":223,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":223,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":225,"right":227,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":5,"right":226,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":226,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":246,"right":248,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":8,"right":245,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":245,"left":230,"right":244,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":230,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":244,"left":240,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":231,"right":239,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":231,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":239,"left":234,"right":238,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":234,"left":13,"right":233,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":233,"left":232,"right":16,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":232,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":237,"right":21,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":237,"left":235,"right":236,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":235,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":236,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":243,"left":242,"right":25,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":242,"left":22,"right":241,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":26,"right":247,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":27,"right":28,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":258,"right":261,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":258,"left":254,"right":257,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":254,"left":253,"right":33,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":29,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":30,"right":251,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":31,"right":32,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":257,"left":34,"right":256,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":256,"left":35,"right":255,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":255,"left":36,"right":37,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":38,"right":260,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":260,"left":39,"right":259,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":40,"right":41,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":442,"left":280,"right":441,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":280,"left":275,"right":279,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":275,"left":267,"right":274,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":267,"left":264,"right":266,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":42,"right":43,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":44,"right":265,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":265,"left":45,"right":46,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":268,"right":273,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":49,"right":272,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":272,"left":270,"right":271,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":269,"right":52,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":269,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":53,"right":54,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":279,"left":55,"right":278,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":56,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":57,"right":276,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":276,"left":58,"right":59,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":441,"left":352,"right":440,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":352,"left":320,"right":351,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":320,"left":288,"right":319,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":285,"right":287,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":60,"right":284,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":284,"left":283,"right":65,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":283,"left":61,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":62,"right":281,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":281,"left":63,"right":64,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":287,"left":286,"right":68,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":286,"left":66,"right":67,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":319,"left":305,"right":318,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":305,"left":301,"right":304,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":297,"right":300,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":297,"left":293,"right":296,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":293,"left":292,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":291,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":289,"right":290,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":69,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":71,"right":72,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":296,"left":294,"right":295,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":294,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":295,"left":77,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":299,"right":82,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":298,"right":81,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":298,"left":79,"right":80,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":302,"right":303,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":302,"left":83,"right":84,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":303,"left":85,"right":86,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent